nsheathed-1117891652/ |access-date=2022-01-01 |date=2003-08-28 |last=Schwarzacher |first=Lukas |work=Variety |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220101040314/https://variety.com/2003/film/news/cruise-unsheathed-1117891652/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=葛大維 |title=阿湯哥 演日本武士肥20磅 700多位記者前展現日化 感謝真田廣之、渡邊謙當教練 |publisher=聯合報 |date=2003-08-29 |page=第D5版 |language=zh-tw}}</ref>。克魯斯此行也和日本時任首相[[小泉纯一郎|小泉純一郎]]在東京的官邸會面<ref>{{cite news|author=洪金珠 |title=武士首映排場大 阿湯哥將再赴東京 |publisher=中國時報 |date=2003-10-14 |page=第D4版 |language=zh-tw}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=林欣若 |title=阿湯與日首相合唱 |publisher=聯合報 |date=2003-08-29 |page=第D5版 |language=zh-tw}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Cruise croons with Japan's PM |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/3188041.stm |access-date=2021-12-26 |date=2003-08-28 |language=en-GB |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130214030/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/3188041.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，兩人一起唱[[埃爾維斯·皮禮士利|埃爾維斯·皮禮士利]]的{{單雙書名號轉換|{{tsl|en|I Want You, I Need You, I Love You}}}}<ref>{{Cite web |title=Tom Cruise sings Elvis duet with Japanese PM |url=https://ew.com/article/2003/08/28/tom-cruise-sings-elvis-duet-japanese-pm/ |access-date=2021-12-26 |date=2003-08-28 |last=Susman |first=Gary |work=Entertainment Weekly |language=en |archive-date=2021-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110102804/https://ew.com/article/2003/08/28/tom-cruise-sings-elvis-duet-japanese-pm/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

