===獎項===
{{main|末代武士獲獎與提名列表}}
《末代武士》獲得多家機構的獎項肯定。2003年12月，本片先後被[[國家評論協會|國家評論協會]]和[[美国电影学会|美國電影學會]]評為年度十大電影之一<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Last Samurai |url=https://nationalboardofreview.org/search/The%20Last%20Samurai/ |access-date=2021-12-16 |work=National Board of Review |language=en-US |archive-date=2021-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211216092711/https://nationalboardofreview.org/search/The%20Last%20Samurai/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NBR">{{Cite web |title=2003 Award Winners |url=https://nationalboardofreview.org/award-years/2003/ |access-date=2021-12-16 |work=National Board of Review |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200429120412/https://nationalboardofreview.org/award-years/2003/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=AFI AWARDS 2003 |url=https://www.afi.com/award/afi-awards-2003/ |access-date=2021-12-29 |work=American Film Institute |language=en |archive-date=2020-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200528140442/https://www.afi.com/award/afi-awards-2003/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="AFIA">{{Cite web |title='Splendor' among AFI's top movies of '03 |url=https://www.today.com/popculture/splendor-among-afis-top-movies-03-wbna3717788 |access-date=2021-12-29 |date=2003-12-15 |work=TODAY.com |language=en |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230022913/https://www.today.com/popculture/splendor-among-afis-top-movies-03-wbna3717788 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。外界將本片列為[[金球獎|金球獎]]和[[奥斯卡金像奖|奧斯卡金像獎]]的熱門之一<ref name="聯合晚報金球">{{cite news|author=唐在揚 |title=金球大戰 很戰爭 很講古 很緋聞 魔戒3、怒海爭鋒、末代武士、冷山… 都被點名 |publisher=聯合晚報 |date=2003-12-06 |page=第11版 |language=zh-tw}}</ref>，而憑片中演出得到好萊塢青睞的渡邊謙則可望入圍[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|奥斯卡最佳男配角奖]]<ref name="民生報真田">{{cite news|author=麥若愚 |title=真田廣之為阿湯哥閉嘴 渡邊謙受好萊塢青睞 可望提名奧斯卡男配角 |publisher=民生報 |date=2003-11-17 |page=第C6版 |language=zh-tw}}</ref>。在接下來的頒獎季中，本片入圍許多影評人協會和電影製作工會的獎項，但得獎的比例不高。2004年1月27日，[[第76届奥斯卡金像奖|第76届奥斯卡金像奖]]的入圍名單公布，本片入圍[[奥斯卡最佳艺术指导奖|最佳藝術指導]]、[[奥斯卡最佳服装设计奖|最佳服裝設計]]和[[奥斯卡最佳音响奖|最佳混音]]三項技術獎項，以及渡邊的[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|最佳男配角]]提名<ref>{{cite news |last=Susman |first=Gary |title=Three-'Ring' Circus |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,574422,00.html |accessdate=2013-10-11 |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Warner |date=2004-01-27 |language=en |archive-date=2013-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004214300/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C574422%2C00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Fernandez |first=Maria Elena |author2=Greg Braxton |title=Dawn's early rite |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2004/jan/28/entertainment/et-fernandez28 |accessdate=2013-10-11 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=2004-01-28 |language=en |archivedate=2013-10-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004215520/http://articles.latimes.com/2004/jan/28/entertainment/et-fernandez28 }}</ref>。《綜藝》雜誌指出，雖然本片看準頒獎季而在年底上映，但並沒有得到[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片獎]]評審的注意<ref>{{Cite web |title=A wing-ding for ‘The King’ |url=https://variety.com/2004/film/awards/a-wing-ding-for-the-king-1117899105/ |access-date=2022-01-01 |date=2004-01-27 |last=Gray |first=Tim |work=Variety |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220101074325/https://variety.com/2004/film/awards/a-wing-ding-for-the-king-1117899105/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

