ss-date=2021-12-20 |work=Findlaw |language=en-US |archive-date=2021-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220151115/https://caselaw.findlaw.com/us-9th-circuit/1526767.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Appeals court gives life to ‘Last Samurai’ idea theft claim |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/appeals-court-life-last-samurai-63972/ |access-date=2021-12-19 |date=2010-12-21 |last=Gardner |first=Eriq |work=The Hollywood Reporter |language=en-US |archive-date=2021-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211219100326/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/appeals-court-life-last-samurai-63972/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年2月14日，美国加利福尼亚中区联邦地区法院駁回對華納兄弟和羅根的指控，因為被告無法證明他們知情<ref>{{Cite web |title=Warner Bros. Wins ‘Last Samurai’ Lawsuit (Exclusive) |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/warner-bros-last-samurai-lawsuit-291433/ |access-date=2021-12-20 |date=2012-02-15 |last=Gardner |first=Eriq |work=The Hollywood Reporter |language=en-US |archive-date=2021-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220101845/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/warner-bros-last-samurai-lawsuit-291433/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，只留下製片人茲維克和赫斯高維基<ref>{{Cite web |title=‘Last Samurai’ Litigation Set for Trial March 20 With Millions at Stake |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/last-samurai-trial-ed-zwick-296417/ |access-date=2021-12-20 |date=2012-03-02 |last=Gardner |first=Eriq |work=The Hollywood Reporter |language=en-US |archive-date=2021-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220143437/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/last-samurai-trial-ed-zwick-296417/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。審判在2012年4月6日舉行，結果是由茲維克和赫斯高維基勝訴，為長年的訴訟畫下句點<ref>{{Cite web |title=Producers Zwick, Herskovitz Win ‘Last Samurai’ Trial Over Allegedly Stolen Script |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/last-samurai-zwick-herskovitz-